WEBVTT

01:48.160 --> 01:51.240
QIHUANG CLINIC

01:56.800 --> 01:58.400
SIZHUKONG, ERMEN

02:15.880 --> 02:19.600
That person also told me
that in the afternoon of June 30th,

02:20.680 --> 02:22.920
those two people would head
to Qihuang Clinic.

02:23.480 --> 02:25.040
He told me to wait for them there.

02:25.960 --> 02:28.280
-A clinic?
-An unlicensed qigong center.

02:28.360 --> 02:29.440
It's probably sealed.

02:30.160 --> 02:31.240
What about the photo?

02:31.320 --> 02:33.280
I burned it.

02:33.880 --> 02:36.080
It's a rule in the gang.

02:38.040 --> 02:39.720
What does "make them disappear" mean?

02:39.800 --> 02:41.160
Kill them?

02:41.240 --> 02:42.840
I don't know either.

02:42.920 --> 02:45.840
He picked up the phone call and vanished.

02:46.960 --> 02:48.720
Officer He.

02:48.800 --> 02:51.000
I never intended to kill anyone.

02:51.080 --> 02:53.000
I just wanted to scare them,

02:53.080 --> 02:56.080
so they would leave Weiyang
and never come back again.

02:56.680 --> 02:58.600
That's disappearing, isn't it?

02:59.120 --> 03:02.200
I waited and waited, but no one ever came.

03:03.200 --> 03:05.040
So, I went out to take a peek.

03:06.440 --> 03:09.320
Then, I heard screams on the floor above.

03:10.000 --> 03:11.320
I then realized that the woman
and the old man

03:11.400 --> 03:13.080
didn't head to the 17th floor,

03:13.160 --> 03:14.320
but the 18th floor.

03:15.400 --> 03:17.600
I went to Pattia before.

03:17.680 --> 03:19.360
I know there is a secret door there.

03:19.880 --> 03:22.680
I figured they might
be hiding on the rooftop.

03:22.760 --> 03:25.160
But I walked around and didn't see them.

03:25.680 --> 03:26.600
Who gave you the keys?

03:29.200 --> 03:30.600
I used some tricks.

03:32.760 --> 03:34.800
Then, I wanted to get out of there.

03:37.240 --> 03:39.040
Then you people came to the 18th floor,

03:39.120 --> 03:41.640
group by group.

03:41.720 --> 03:43.840
I couldn't run away.

03:46.160 --> 03:49.080
I waited until the sun set.

03:51.880 --> 03:53.840
I couldn't stand it anymore.

03:53.920 --> 03:55.480
So, I let it out.

03:56.000 --> 03:58.160
I was all sweaty and dirty,

03:58.760 --> 04:00.040
and I thought

04:00.120 --> 04:02.480
I couldn't just suffer this for nothing.

04:02.560 --> 04:05.120
I must get the balance of the payment.

04:05.200 --> 04:07.880
I must show the gang how good I am.

04:13.800 --> 04:16.399
So, I bluffed.

04:17.000 --> 04:19.760
I grabbed a bag,
made myself a bloody cloak,

04:20.920 --> 04:22.640
and told everyone
that I had killed two people.

04:29.400 --> 04:30.720
Then, the blood in the bag…

04:30.800 --> 04:31.880
It's all chicken blood.

04:32.480 --> 04:33.880
Test it if you don't trust me.

04:33.960 --> 04:36.480
If it's human blood,
just shoot me on the spot.

04:47.320 --> 04:48.560
What were you doing in 407?

04:53.760 --> 04:55.160
Who gave you the job?

04:56.440 --> 04:57.400
I don't know who he is.

04:57.920 --> 05:00.440
-How much did he offer?
-Forty-thousand yuan.

05:00.520 --> 05:02.720
But he still owes me
the balance of 30,000 yuan.

05:02.800 --> 05:04.600
You can't even recognize him.

05:04.680 --> 05:06.520
How are you supposed to ask him to pay?

05:06.600 --> 05:09.920
He said he'd call me after the job.

05:10.000 --> 05:10.880
Buddy.

05:10.960 --> 05:13.200
You killed them.

05:13.720 --> 05:15.200
Why would he contact you?

05:16.040 --> 05:18.600
So that you can turn yourself in
to the police?

05:20.280 --> 05:21.720
Gosh.

05:23.960 --> 05:26.200
Did anyone see you when you did it?

05:29.640 --> 05:30.600
Answer me!

05:32.520 --> 05:33.760
I think

05:37.360 --> 05:39.080
I saw someone when I was leaving.

05:39.160 --> 05:40.240
You think?

05:56.760 --> 05:58.920
Idiot! And you can sleep
at night like this?

05:59.000 --> 06:01.600
Find that witness and silence him.

06:01.680 --> 06:05.240
That old man in 407 saw me.

06:05.880 --> 06:07.200
I had to silence him.

06:07.880 --> 06:10.000
Someone still owes me 30,000 yuan.

06:10.080 --> 06:12.280
If someone tells the police,

06:12.360 --> 06:14.160
I will be busted.

06:14.760 --> 06:16.960
I was very polite to him.

06:17.680 --> 06:19.120
Yes.

06:19.640 --> 06:21.560
He was quite polite.

06:22.080 --> 06:23.960
But really, I've never seen him before.

06:24.640 --> 06:26.120
Never.

06:26.200 --> 06:28.040
Last night,

06:28.120 --> 06:30.440
I was reading a detective novel in my bed.

06:30.520 --> 06:34.000
I was captivated by it, and it kept me up.

06:34.080 --> 06:35.080
I couldn't sleep,

06:35.160 --> 06:37.320
so I thought I could climb some stairs

06:37.400 --> 06:39.480
and sweat a little before I went to bed.

06:39.560 --> 06:42.240
As soon as I opened
the door to the staircase,

06:44.040 --> 06:46.440
I felt so drowsy.

06:46.520 --> 06:49.400
My eyelids were heavy.
I could barely keep them open.

06:49.480 --> 06:50.880
So, I went back to sleep.

06:50.960 --> 06:52.800
I didn't see anything.

06:54.080 --> 06:55.160
I didn't see him.

06:57.040 --> 06:59.240
You love to read detective novels?

06:59.320 --> 07:00.240
Yes.

07:00.320 --> 07:01.200
You too?

07:01.280 --> 07:02.240
Yes.

07:02.960 --> 07:04.680
We have the same hobby.

07:04.760 --> 07:06.520
What kind of detective novels?

07:06.600 --> 07:07.840
The classical European ones or--

07:09.440 --> 07:10.360
Du Mandun.

07:10.440 --> 07:12.880
If you didn't see Jin Manlang,
why did you call the police?

07:13.640 --> 07:16.400
I'm a fan of mysteries.

07:17.240 --> 07:18.360
Did you notice?

07:18.880 --> 07:22.240
Yesterday, someone disappeared
in a locked room on the 18th floor.

07:22.320 --> 07:25.720
Today, everyone is singing
that nursery song.

07:25.800 --> 07:30.280
Isn't that just like the prelude
to a murder in every detective novel?

07:31.200 --> 07:32.840
Speak plainly, please.

07:32.920 --> 07:34.680
Continue. I understand everything.

07:34.760 --> 07:36.600
-Okay. Listen.
-Sure.

07:36.680 --> 07:40.240
I thought the whole thing
could never be this simple.

07:40.320 --> 07:42.400
-At first…
-You didn't even see a shadow.

07:42.480 --> 07:43.840
Who says I didn't see anything?

07:44.440 --> 07:46.520
I saw her clearly.

07:46.600 --> 07:48.400
I saw the woman twice.

07:50.160 --> 07:52.120
I saw her carrying… Like…

07:53.000 --> 07:55.040
Relax. Tell us one by one.

07:57.920 --> 07:59.400
I first saw her

08:00.120 --> 08:02.960
in the morning several days ago.

08:03.480 --> 08:07.000
Right at the corner of the staircase.

08:17.800 --> 08:21.400
The second time I saw her was yesterday.

08:22.000 --> 08:26.520
I was playing gateball
at the park with Meng and Wang.

08:26.600 --> 08:30.080
I saw the woman walking by
while carrying an old man.

08:30.160 --> 08:31.960
She looked exactly like the woman

08:32.039 --> 08:34.840
I had met on the staircase
several days ago.

08:34.919 --> 08:36.360
Are you sure they were identical?

08:38.960 --> 08:40.600
Try to recall.

08:40.679 --> 08:42.960
Did anything stand out
when you saw the woman?

08:43.480 --> 08:45.240
-Anything that stood out?
-Yes.

08:56.560 --> 08:59.400
She had medical patches on her wrists.

08:59.480 --> 09:01.560
Over here and over here.

09:05.560 --> 09:09.880
These are probably marks
left by medical patches.

09:13.680 --> 09:14.560
It matches.

09:15.160 --> 09:16.840
How so?

09:16.920 --> 09:18.320
The medical patch has her name on it?

09:19.920 --> 09:21.280
This is an important lead.

09:21.360 --> 09:23.440
What kind of woman would use
medical patches on her wrists?

09:23.520 --> 09:25.360
It must have something to do with her job.

09:26.000 --> 09:27.960
That's just your opinion.

09:28.040 --> 09:30.840
I think she might have injured
her wrists while she carried things.

09:30.920 --> 09:32.920
Or she might have a scar
that she didn't want anyone to see.

09:33.000 --> 09:34.320
The possibilities are endless.

09:34.400 --> 09:36.400
Yes. You're absolutely right.

09:36.480 --> 09:38.880
All these possibilities
are possible clues to this murder.

09:38.960 --> 09:40.880
Must you get us a murder case?

09:40.960 --> 09:42.600
Someone has hired a man to kill them.

09:42.680 --> 09:44.160
How is this not a murder?

09:45.640 --> 09:48.520
Officer, is this truly a murder?

10:03.520 --> 10:06.920
We analyzed the blood
in the bag and on the rooftop.

10:07.000 --> 10:08.040
It's not human blood.

10:08.800 --> 10:11.440
The saliva sample from the cigarette butt
matches Jin Manlang.

10:14.760 --> 10:17.680
It seems like someone
has tried so hard for nothing.

10:17.760 --> 10:21.280
They probably hope the witnesses are lying
so that they can continue investigating.

10:23.200 --> 10:24.360
I know they are not lying.

10:24.440 --> 10:25.440
How do you know?

10:25.520 --> 10:27.400
Eyes are the window to your soul.

10:27.480 --> 10:29.360
If you look to the left when you speak,
it means that you're recalling.

10:29.440 --> 10:30.960
If you look to the right,
it means you're making things up.

10:31.040 --> 10:33.120
When Jin Manlang and Mr. Du were speaking,

10:33.200 --> 10:34.680
they were looking to the left.

10:35.360 --> 10:36.480
What about the photo?

10:37.920 --> 10:39.760
I burned it.

10:43.280 --> 10:44.960
I first saw her

10:48.360 --> 10:49.640
in the…

10:50.160 --> 10:52.680
They did not have
the telltale sign of lying.

10:58.480 --> 11:00.520
Smarty pants who like to lecture.

11:00.600 --> 11:02.120
They did not lie,

11:02.200 --> 11:04.080
but that doesn't mean
the two missing people

11:04.160 --> 11:05.480
are not in danger.

11:06.600 --> 11:08.000
Can you two stop arguing?

11:09.600 --> 11:11.080
I analyzed everything in the box.

11:11.160 --> 11:12.200
Nothing new.

11:12.280 --> 11:14.880
Keep it or return it, it's your call.

11:16.120 --> 11:17.320
I still have work to do.

11:24.920 --> 11:27.520
THE GREEK COFFIN MYSTERY

11:38.200 --> 11:41.040
MISSING PERSON

12:04.960 --> 12:06.000
MISSING PERSON

12:06.080 --> 12:09.200
Why is this poster still here?

12:10.200 --> 12:11.400
Isn't it weird?

12:11.960 --> 12:13.520
Let me show you something weirder.

12:25.600 --> 12:28.080
‎DEMOLITION

12:35.480 --> 12:36.520
Does this look familiar to you?

12:41.240 --> 12:43.880
Does this belong to Jin Manlang?

12:51.760 --> 12:54.760
I returned everything back then.

12:54.840 --> 12:57.760
This mooncake box belongs to Wolfie.

12:58.920 --> 13:01.600
This detective novel belongs to Du Mandun.

13:02.800 --> 13:07.240
Why are their things
kept together in the same place?

13:08.360 --> 13:09.600
And look at the poster.

13:10.400 --> 13:13.920
The paper and the ink are both new.

13:15.960 --> 13:17.400
Weird, isn't it?

13:18.000 --> 13:19.240
It has been so many years.

13:20.560 --> 13:23.600
I never believed
that Yuanlongli was haunted.

13:24.320 --> 13:25.160
YUXI CIGARETTE

13:25.240 --> 13:27.200
Someone must be behind all of this.

13:59.840 --> 14:01.040
407.

14:01.560 --> 14:03.120
Du Mandun's unit.

14:03.640 --> 14:05.000
He moved out several months ago.

14:29.520 --> 14:30.840
So, it was all a false alarm.

14:34.480 --> 14:38.080
Du Mandun moved out,
but he didn't take his books.

14:47.720 --> 14:50.440
I remember he was quite invested

14:50.520 --> 14:52.400
in the missing persons case back then.

14:52.480 --> 14:54.840
He even discussed some conspiracies
or locked rooms with you.

14:55.560 --> 14:56.760
Sir,

14:56.840 --> 14:58.320
ever since we set foot into Yuanlongli,

14:58.400 --> 15:00.400
you've been mentioning
that particular case.

15:00.480 --> 15:02.280
What does it have to do
with the missing kid?

15:03.000 --> 15:05.400
It has everything to do with it.
They are both missing person cases.

15:05.480 --> 15:06.400
So?

15:07.480 --> 15:09.560
So, we're looking for them.

15:10.720 --> 15:11.920
Sir,

15:12.000 --> 15:13.440
I came to Weiyang
to write the lesson plan,

15:13.520 --> 15:14.960
and my schedule is tight enough.

15:17.320 --> 15:18.840
Three floors left.

15:18.920 --> 15:20.440
You gave me your word.

15:20.520 --> 15:22.600
Now keep your promise.

15:33.320 --> 15:34.400
Let's go.

15:35.120 --> 15:36.080
Let's go.

15:45.680 --> 15:48.360
WEIYANG PUBLIC SECURITY BUREAU
NANSHAN BRANCH

16:00.760 --> 16:01.600
I already signed.

16:01.680 --> 16:02.880
Please sign it, too.

16:04.760 --> 16:06.320
CRIMINAL CASE REGISTRATION FORM

16:06.400 --> 16:08.600
Since you always go to Qu Dahai,
ask him to sign it.

16:09.200 --> 16:10.560
He doesn't have the power.

16:11.880 --> 16:12.760
Neither do I.

16:13.360 --> 16:15.440
Don't worry. After you sign it,
I'll be in charge of it.

16:15.520 --> 16:17.800
You're a rookie. How
can you be in charge of it?

16:17.880 --> 16:20.000
Our priority now is not to file a case.

16:20.080 --> 16:22.240
It's to find those two people.

16:31.640 --> 16:33.320
If you won't sign the registration form,

16:33.400 --> 16:34.440
can you sign this?

16:34.520 --> 16:35.360
EVIDENCE SUBPOENA REQUEST FORM

16:36.360 --> 16:37.200
What is this?

16:38.000 --> 16:39.720
The woman used medical patches.

16:39.800 --> 16:41.640
I want to check the hospital records

16:41.720 --> 16:43.800
to see if someone
injured their wrists lately.

16:45.560 --> 16:47.520
You don't have
any real-life experience, do you?

16:47.600 --> 16:49.680
Do you think

16:49.760 --> 16:51.240
they will go to the hospital
for a small injury like this?

16:52.520 --> 16:54.600
Where else could she
have gotten the patches?

16:54.680 --> 16:55.880
In a pharmacy.

16:55.960 --> 16:57.120
In a clinic.

16:57.200 --> 16:59.440
Many people are selling
common medications.

16:59.520 --> 17:01.440
Following your method, I can sign it,

17:01.520 --> 17:04.040
and you still won't
find anything after years.

17:04.119 --> 17:05.319
Then, how should we proceed?

17:05.400 --> 17:07.720
Put up posters and wait on the bench?

17:07.800 --> 17:09.520
Are you lecturing me right now?

17:09.599 --> 17:11.920
At least I caught someone
after waiting the whole day.

17:12.000 --> 17:13.520
What did you find?

17:13.599 --> 17:15.160
Chicken blood?

17:15.240 --> 17:17.480
Duck blood can be added to a hotpot.
But chicken blood? It's useless.

17:17.560 --> 17:18.800
Enough.

17:18.880 --> 17:20.640
-Will you sign it or not?
-No!

17:25.440 --> 17:26.520
Criminal department.

17:26.599 --> 17:27.520
Dad!

17:30.120 --> 17:31.720
Yes. It's me.

17:32.760 --> 17:34.080
You haven't come back in so long.

17:34.160 --> 17:36.640
It's getting harder to see you now.

17:37.760 --> 17:39.560
I'll come back soon.

17:39.640 --> 17:40.720
Again?

17:40.800 --> 17:44.080
Your soon is getting absurdly long.

17:44.160 --> 17:45.760
Kiddo,

17:46.320 --> 17:48.600
I recently ran into a troublemaker.

17:48.680 --> 17:49.760
He keeps pestering me.

17:50.440 --> 17:52.000
Then, buy me a bottle of Coke.

17:52.080 --> 17:54.040
Don't tell Mom.

17:54.120 --> 17:55.440
Sure.

17:55.960 --> 17:57.880
Wait. Mom wants to talk to you.

17:58.400 --> 17:59.240
Xiaohe.

17:59.320 --> 18:00.280
Go back to your room.

18:00.360 --> 18:01.760
He Yuanhang, where are you?

18:03.560 --> 18:05.160
I'm working now.

18:05.240 --> 18:07.720
I need to work hard to impress my boss.

18:07.800 --> 18:09.760
That way, I can stay
in the criminal department.

18:09.840 --> 18:12.040
Are you trying to get back
to the police station again?

18:12.880 --> 18:15.080
Who says that? That's impossible.

18:15.160 --> 18:16.800
I met Qu Dahai today.

18:16.880 --> 18:18.000
He told me that.

18:18.080 --> 18:20.600
-He said you'd return next week.
-Qu Dahai.

18:21.200 --> 18:23.760
Listen. He's trying to break us up.

18:23.840 --> 18:26.720
He can't wait to return
to the police station.

18:27.440 --> 18:28.800
What? He Yuanhang!

18:28.880 --> 18:29.880
It's noisy here.

18:29.960 --> 18:30.960
The lines are mixed up.

18:31.040 --> 18:34.320
-Officer He said only six days left till…
-Till I catch…

18:34.400 --> 18:36.240
Wait. It's noisy here.

18:36.320 --> 18:38.000
Only six days left till he goes back to…

18:38.640 --> 18:39.960
Give me a moment.

18:45.520 --> 18:46.360
Don't worry.

18:46.440 --> 18:49.840
I'll work hard to stay
in the criminal department.

18:49.920 --> 18:51.200
I have to hang up now.

18:51.280 --> 18:52.800
I have a meeting soon. Okay.

18:54.040 --> 18:56.400
Getting bolder now, huh?

19:11.880 --> 19:12.720
Let's go.

19:12.800 --> 19:14.480
You go ahead. I need to work.

19:14.560 --> 19:15.760
Who says it's not about work?

19:15.840 --> 19:16.880
We have a new lead.

19:17.920 --> 19:18.800
Hey!

19:18.880 --> 19:19.760
Wait for me.

19:24.720 --> 19:25.800
Where are my shoes?

19:30.480 --> 19:31.960
You have five minutes

19:32.040 --> 19:33.600
to get yourself some new outfits
at the night market.

19:52.600 --> 19:53.440
Sir, buy some leather shoes.

19:53.520 --> 19:55.120
They are all genuine leather. Take a look.

19:55.200 --> 19:56.240
We have a clearance sale today.

19:56.320 --> 19:58.000
Everything is cheap. Trust me.

19:58.080 --> 19:59.960
Sir, you have great taste.

20:02.160 --> 20:04.120
Double Fish Heels. They are branded.

20:04.200 --> 20:05.520
Are they for your girlfriend?

20:08.080 --> 20:09.040
Sir.

20:09.560 --> 20:10.800
Come. Take a look.

20:11.320 --> 20:12.960
I also have stirrup pants. Get them too.

20:13.040 --> 20:15.520
Blue and red, as beautiful as you get.

20:17.480 --> 20:19.040
Sir, help me out, will you?

20:19.120 --> 20:20.360
I'll forever remember your generosity.

20:50.800 --> 20:51.800
Did you gain some common sense?

20:59.760 --> 21:00.800
Boat orchids.

21:00.880 --> 21:02.080
You splurged.

21:03.600 --> 21:04.440
It's to compensate someone.

21:06.840 --> 21:08.160
Compensate someone?

21:31.520 --> 21:34.480
You're somehow attached
to these old sandals?

21:37.640 --> 21:39.480
It's to compensate someone too.

21:39.560 --> 21:40.920
It's to compensate someone too?

21:41.000 --> 21:42.360
You have only worked for two days.

21:42.440 --> 21:43.320
You didn't earn anything,

21:43.400 --> 21:44.400
but you have to compensate
for losses already.

21:45.200 --> 21:46.040
Well done.

21:55.640 --> 21:57.920
Oh. Guess what I saw in the night market.

21:59.160 --> 22:01.440
The blue leather heels
worn by the missing woman.

22:01.960 --> 22:03.360
They are called Double Fish Heels.

22:03.440 --> 22:05.560
A renowned brand, apparently.
Expensive too.

22:05.640 --> 22:06.960
They come in different colors.

22:07.040 --> 22:09.720
Red, black, and even white.

22:11.360 --> 22:14.520
Why didn't you buy something
for your intelligence?

22:14.600 --> 22:17.480
Branded goods in a night market?
How authentic can they be?

22:25.920 --> 22:26.840
Hey. What are you doing?

22:28.480 --> 22:30.920
Don't touch it.
If you break it, I'll be in trouble.

22:34.360 --> 22:36.160
Is this your daughter's?

22:36.960 --> 22:38.240
Yes.

22:38.320 --> 22:39.760
How old is she?

22:41.360 --> 22:43.360
Eight years old. Year 3.

22:44.600 --> 22:48.080
Is she the reason why you don't want
to stay in the criminal department?

22:50.320 --> 22:51.880
I know it wouldn't be because of you.

22:52.600 --> 22:53.880
Stop asking questions.

22:54.520 --> 22:55.560
It's none of your business.

22:59.080 --> 23:00.080
You studied in Beijing.

23:00.160 --> 23:02.080
But you are assigned to Weiyang.

23:02.160 --> 23:03.320
Is your family okay with it?

23:04.920 --> 23:06.040
You checked my file.

23:07.000 --> 23:08.000
I didn't.

23:08.080 --> 23:10.000
But when Captain Feng
gave me an apprentice,

23:10.080 --> 23:11.000
I had to check what I'd be getting.

23:11.080 --> 23:12.360
Let me reiterate.

23:12.440 --> 23:14.160
-I am not your apprentice.
-All right.

23:14.800 --> 23:16.320
Won't you get sick of nagging,
my dear apprentice?

23:16.400 --> 23:17.240
I…

23:23.760 --> 23:26.240
You look so pampered.

23:26.760 --> 23:28.520
Your family must be rich.

23:29.600 --> 23:31.400
What do your parents do?

23:44.680 --> 23:51.560
SHANCHENG HOTPOT

24:11.200 --> 24:12.440
He's quite handsome,

24:12.520 --> 24:15.720
but his fashion sense is a bit lacking.

24:15.800 --> 24:17.800
He is dressed like an old man.

24:21.880 --> 24:24.240
I'll bring some drinks over.

24:26.920 --> 24:27.760
What do you want?

24:28.840 --> 24:31.200
Whatever you bring me.

24:37.280 --> 24:39.800
I didn't know
it was your number on the poster.

24:40.400 --> 24:42.320
If I had known it,
I wouldn't have called you.

24:44.560 --> 24:46.080
I'm just helping out.

24:46.160 --> 24:47.960
Their relatives are eager to find them.

24:48.480 --> 24:49.520
Relatives?

24:58.640 --> 24:59.480
Thanks, cutie.

25:00.400 --> 25:01.880
You're… You're welcome.

25:05.560 --> 25:07.080
MISSING PERSON

25:07.160 --> 25:08.520
Do you know them?

25:14.000 --> 25:17.120
The woman on the poster was my colleague.

25:21.000 --> 25:22.320
Colleagues?

25:22.400 --> 25:24.720
What's her name? What kind of work?

25:25.520 --> 25:27.080
Ex-colleagues.

25:28.080 --> 25:28.920
Her name is Mengmeng.

25:29.720 --> 25:31.240
What kind of work?

25:33.840 --> 25:34.760
A massage parlor.

25:37.240 --> 25:39.760
No wonder she used medical patches.

25:41.880 --> 25:44.000
What's her surname? Her full name, please.

25:44.080 --> 25:46.200
Mengmeng is just a nickname.

25:46.280 --> 25:49.680
Masseuses never use their real names.

25:50.520 --> 25:51.840
Ignore him.

25:51.920 --> 25:53.840
He's just a rookie who knows nothing.

25:53.920 --> 25:56.000
Just share your information with me.

25:56.880 --> 25:59.000
Cutie. Let me tell you the truth.

25:59.800 --> 26:00.920
It's a massage parlor,

26:01.000 --> 26:03.040
but we do all sorts of things there.

26:03.120 --> 26:05.280
So, the girls there
are from other regions.

26:05.360 --> 26:07.400
Mengmeng is the only local there.

26:07.920 --> 26:09.440
I only know

26:09.520 --> 26:12.080
that her father is quite sick.

26:12.160 --> 26:13.640
She can't leave Weiyang.

26:14.680 --> 26:15.760
Have you seen her father?

26:17.600 --> 26:20.160
I guess it was the guy she was carrying.

26:21.920 --> 26:24.040
Does Mengmeng have other relatives?

26:27.680 --> 26:29.600
Didn't you tell me her relatives
were looking for her?

26:31.360 --> 26:33.600
Police officers and citizens are a family.

26:33.680 --> 26:36.440
I can't find her relatives,
but I'll help them find her first.

26:37.800 --> 26:39.560
Officer He. The police can't find them.

26:39.640 --> 26:41.200
Let alone a citizen like me.

26:46.560 --> 26:48.880
Where is the parlor?

26:48.960 --> 26:50.120
What is the name?

26:50.200 --> 26:51.360
Ask him.

26:51.440 --> 26:52.840
He raided the place.

26:57.680 --> 26:58.760
Pattia.

26:59.320 --> 27:01.680
Cutie. You've been there before?

27:02.280 --> 27:03.640
How come I've never seen you?

27:03.720 --> 27:06.440
No, not at all. I… I just came to Weiyang.

27:08.480 --> 27:11.800
I just want to know if Mengmeng
is close to anyone else.

27:11.880 --> 27:13.960
She is the quiet type.

27:14.040 --> 27:15.360
Quite dull.

27:15.440 --> 27:17.680
When she was not working,
she would make small talk with me.

27:19.360 --> 27:21.880
A rich man often asked for her.

27:21.960 --> 27:24.320
Sometimes, he would take her with him.

27:26.360 --> 27:28.080
Rich man? What's his name?

27:28.680 --> 27:30.000
Sun, I think.

27:30.080 --> 27:32.800
I don't know his name.

27:35.400 --> 27:36.520
Try to recall.

27:36.600 --> 27:38.520
He asked for Mengmeng, not me.

27:38.600 --> 27:41.440
Besides, who uses their real name
in this kind of place?

27:42.920 --> 27:44.960
Do you know where Mengmeng went afterward?

27:45.840 --> 27:48.840
She went to a foot massage parlor

27:48.920 --> 27:51.080
in Tenglong Street.

27:51.680 --> 27:54.600
I think it's called… Muse.

28:14.520 --> 28:18.080
People in my line of work
are used to moving frequently.

28:18.600 --> 28:20.160
Many went missing too,

28:21.040 --> 28:23.200
but no one cares.

28:32.800 --> 28:35.760
I don't care if others care about it,
but we will see it through.

28:35.840 --> 28:37.320
Don't worry about it.

28:41.040 --> 28:42.520
Allow me to thank you
on behalf of Mengmeng.

28:46.920 --> 28:48.200
No need. It's our job.

28:57.280 --> 28:58.600
Dig in. It's on me today.

28:59.920 --> 29:01.360
What do you like to eat?

29:02.200 --> 29:03.280
Anything.

29:03.360 --> 29:04.200
Then, I'll add everything in.

29:09.240 --> 29:13.040
SHANCHENG HOTPOT

29:19.480 --> 29:21.240
Thank you for providing
crucial information.

29:21.320 --> 29:22.800
We can help you claim the reward.

29:23.880 --> 29:25.480
I don't want your money.

29:26.440 --> 29:28.640
Remember. You owe me a meal of hotpot,

29:28.720 --> 29:29.720
cutie.

29:31.880 --> 29:32.920
Wait.

29:34.800 --> 29:37.680
Is your father Su Qingyou?

29:48.160 --> 29:50.960
This must be yours.

30:00.080 --> 30:01.880
I've been looking for this photo.

30:01.960 --> 30:03.000
Where did you find it?

30:03.920 --> 30:06.640
Eighteenth floor of Yuanlongli.
Where Pattia was.

30:09.520 --> 30:11.040
SU QINGYOU

30:22.200 --> 30:23.360
Cutie,

30:23.440 --> 30:25.840
when you're free,
you must visit the parlor.

30:25.920 --> 30:27.480
I'll give you a nice surprise.

30:28.280 --> 30:29.320
See you.

30:34.400 --> 30:37.320
Are you here to investigate
the case or to flirt?

30:38.360 --> 30:39.400
Go now.

30:40.560 --> 30:41.640
Where to?

30:41.720 --> 30:42.920
To find the surprise.

30:48.760 --> 30:51.400
MUSE FOOT MASSAGE

30:59.280 --> 31:00.240
‎-Sir!
‎-Dear sir!

31:00.840 --> 31:03.520
‎-Come on in!
‎-We waited for so long.

31:06.040 --> 31:07.960
You will go in through the main entrance.

31:08.040 --> 31:08.960
I'll take the rear entrance.

31:09.040 --> 31:10.960
If something happens, we'll surround them.

31:14.680 --> 31:15.600
Wait.

31:15.680 --> 31:18.720
When you're inside,
do you know what to say?

31:18.800 --> 31:20.680
Say what? I'll speak
like I normally would.

31:22.880 --> 31:24.160
I know.

31:24.960 --> 31:26.840
Since you're so approachable,

31:26.920 --> 31:28.640
why did you ask me to go in?

31:29.160 --> 31:30.840
I'm worried they might recognize me.

31:35.920 --> 31:37.240
Get that out of your mind!

31:37.320 --> 31:38.960
Don't you know what I did?

31:39.040 --> 31:40.240
Go now.

31:52.800 --> 31:56.360
MUSE FOOT MASSAGE

32:03.280 --> 32:05.360
Be patient. It's fine,
even if they are new.

32:05.880 --> 32:08.360
There are some over there.
A few girls over there.

32:10.720 --> 32:12.040
Hi, Mister.

32:12.120 --> 32:13.080
First time here?

32:14.880 --> 32:15.800
Yes.

32:17.800 --> 32:19.080
Come in.

32:19.160 --> 32:20.880
-Dear sir!
-Sir! Is it your first time here?

32:20.960 --> 32:22.040
You want something?

32:22.120 --> 32:23.080
Don't be shy.

32:23.160 --> 32:25.000
Yes, don't be shy.

32:25.720 --> 32:27.520
The price is over there.
Pick anything you like.

32:40.880 --> 32:42.360
Anything will do.

32:44.760 --> 32:45.640
Anything will do?

32:45.720 --> 32:48.280
So which service then? Take a look.

32:49.840 --> 32:50.760
You know what?

32:51.600 --> 32:52.880
I want Mengmeng to massage me.

32:56.520 --> 32:57.360
Mengmeng?

32:57.440 --> 33:00.200
She is sick today.

33:00.280 --> 33:01.720
She took sick leave.

33:03.160 --> 33:05.560
Pick another one.
The girls here are very friendly.

33:05.640 --> 33:06.960
Exactly.

33:07.040 --> 33:08.000
Pick another one.

33:10.400 --> 33:12.200
Where is your boss?

33:14.360 --> 33:15.200
Behind.

33:16.160 --> 33:17.240
I'll get her for you.

33:17.320 --> 33:18.320
Okay.

33:18.840 --> 33:20.120
Give me a second.

33:22.280 --> 33:23.280
Give me a second.

33:27.160 --> 33:28.160
Raid!

33:28.240 --> 33:29.960
Raid! Raid!

33:30.040 --> 33:32.160
Raid!

33:36.800 --> 33:37.760
ROOM 3

33:47.080 --> 33:49.000
Pervert! Pervert!

33:49.080 --> 33:50.480
Pervert!

34:00.440 --> 34:01.240
Stop!

34:04.320 --> 34:05.160
You still won't stop?

34:18.159 --> 34:19.360
Officer.

34:19.440 --> 34:22.199
I just washed my feet. They are clean.

34:24.600 --> 34:25.880
Ms. Zhao.

34:25.960 --> 34:28.760
I spilled the feet water
on his face just now.

34:29.440 --> 34:30.600
Is it funny?

34:31.760 --> 34:33.080
Tell me.

34:33.159 --> 34:35.600
When did all of you last see Mengmeng?

34:36.239 --> 34:37.560
I don't know.

34:39.840 --> 34:42.440
She stopped coming to work three days ago.

34:43.760 --> 34:44.880
Why?

34:45.840 --> 34:47.600
Did she run into trouble
on her last day here?

34:47.679 --> 34:48.639
I don't know.

34:49.960 --> 34:51.480
What could possibly happen here?

34:51.560 --> 34:54.159
And how would I know
why she stopped coming to work?

34:55.040 --> 34:58.040
Did she meet any clients
on her last day here?

35:00.000 --> 35:01.760
I don't know.

35:01.840 --> 35:03.080
No one picked her.

35:03.160 --> 35:05.080
She didn't earn anything,
so she stopped coming.

35:05.160 --> 35:06.000
You…

35:09.240 --> 35:10.840
First, you said you didn't know.

35:10.920 --> 35:12.640
Now, you said no one picked her.

35:12.720 --> 35:15.040
So, do you know something or not?

35:15.720 --> 35:16.960
Sir.

35:18.520 --> 35:20.200
"I don't know" is my catchphrase.

35:20.920 --> 35:24.000
Mengmeng and I are colleagues.

35:24.080 --> 35:25.120
She's like my subordinate.

35:25.720 --> 35:29.400
Why would she tell me about her troubles?

35:30.080 --> 35:30.960
Ask them if you don't trust me.

35:31.040 --> 35:33.840
Would you come to me
if you run into trouble?

35:37.520 --> 35:38.680
See?

35:45.600 --> 35:46.600
All right.

35:47.440 --> 35:49.720
Surely, you must know
Mengmeng's real name.

35:51.760 --> 35:53.040
Of course.

35:59.800 --> 36:01.280
NRIC PHOTOCOPY

36:06.560 --> 36:09.280
XU MENG

36:09.360 --> 36:15.280
DAJIANCHANG NEIGHBORHOOD

36:17.600 --> 36:21.080
Why didn't you tell the others
to raid the foot massage parlor?

36:21.880 --> 36:23.280
You know nothing.

36:23.840 --> 36:26.240
It's not the time to retrieve the net yet.

36:27.000 --> 36:29.480
Let's wait till we find
Xu Meng and her father.

36:50.680 --> 36:51.720
Stop searching.

36:52.480 --> 36:54.120
It should be that unit.

36:57.880 --> 37:03.240
DIE

37:25.720 --> 37:26.840
A putrid stench.

37:32.280 --> 37:33.440
Corpse?

37:35.320 --> 37:36.520
Not sure.

37:44.560 --> 37:46.080
It's locked from the inside.

37:46.160 --> 37:47.960
I can't open it without the keys.

38:00.600 --> 38:02.240
Don't just stand there.

38:02.320 --> 38:03.680
Call for backup

38:04.280 --> 38:05.800
and ask them to break the door.

38:12.160 --> 38:13.200
Do you know how to do this?

38:13.800 --> 38:16.840
We learned how to pick locks at school.

38:16.920 --> 38:19.000
They sure taught you
many practical things.

38:25.720 --> 38:26.760
Are you doing this on purpose?

38:31.400 --> 38:32.800
Listen.

38:32.880 --> 38:35.560
Once we get back, make sure we follow
the due process for breaking in.

38:42.080 --> 38:43.280
‎FOR RENT

39:11.440 --> 39:14.400
The meat is all rotten.

39:14.480 --> 39:15.560
Look.

39:15.640 --> 39:17.080
They didn't even put the food away.

39:17.160 --> 39:18.720
Probably left in a hurry.

39:23.160 --> 39:24.320
I only have one.

39:38.440 --> 39:39.760
Poor thing.

39:52.640 --> 39:53.880
Why did they break the wall?

39:55.480 --> 39:56.600
Officer He.

39:58.480 --> 39:59.680
Size 37.

40:05.240 --> 40:06.200
DOUBLE FISH

40:07.880 --> 40:09.160
Double Fish Heels.

40:10.920 --> 40:12.000
Authenticity logo.

40:12.600 --> 40:13.960
It's expensive to get the real ones.

40:31.920 --> 40:33.520
Why did they break the wall?

40:35.160 --> 40:37.200
To move the cupboard out?

40:46.880 --> 40:47.720
So skinny.

40:48.680 --> 40:50.520
No wonder Xu Meng
could carry her father on her back.

40:51.920 --> 40:53.000
The father's teeth are quite unique.

40:59.880 --> 41:01.800
PENICILLIN V TABLETS

41:02.920 --> 41:03.800
That's odd.

41:03.880 --> 41:05.160
What is?

41:07.120 --> 41:10.960
I saw in the security footage
that her father was holding a cigarette.

41:11.040 --> 41:12.560
It looks like a cigarette.

41:13.320 --> 41:14.600
But he has a lung disease.

41:14.680 --> 41:15.920
Why would he be smoking?

41:17.520 --> 41:19.520
They have done weirder things.

41:19.600 --> 41:21.000
Perhaps he thought it wasn't worth it.

41:21.080 --> 41:23.000
Just smoke and drink however he wanted.

41:34.360 --> 41:35.640
HOUSEHOLD REGISTER

41:35.720 --> 41:36.560
HOUSEHOLD REGISTER, SAVINGS ACCOUNT

41:39.160 --> 41:41.480
REGISTER OF PERMANENT RESIDENT, XU ZHIHONG

41:41.560 --> 41:43.080
REGISTER OF PERMANENT RESIDENT, XU MENG

42:07.200 --> 42:08.720
Bowls?

42:08.800 --> 42:10.880
I've seen this brand in a mall in Beijing.

42:11.480 --> 42:14.240
This dress is probably
more expensive than this flat.

42:15.840 --> 42:19.400
It doesn't feel like something
Xu Meng would wear.

42:19.480 --> 42:20.760
It doesn't match her style.

42:22.040 --> 42:23.920
You sure know your fashion.

42:55.960 --> 42:57.080
Police!
